      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-373389077394698207",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "まとめ"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h2"
    },
    {
      "_key": "summary-fe3ee4d2-1438-4a56-9201-bace2cfaa205",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "summary-span-119773a8-51c7-4395-8296-bdcdd7e93c1f",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "看護助手から介護職へ転職する人が多い理由でお伝えした内容を振り返ると、日々の現場で大切にしたいポイントが幾つか見えてきます。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "summary-b67e04e8-a94d-42ea-ac95-9a7c9990624b",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "summary-span-06a64ab7-b13f-4c3e-91c2-ba2cb5a73b1d",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "すぐに試しやすい行動のヒントは次の通りです。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "summary-bullet-8d5d3cbd-e0f9-4cbf-9ff1-5caa3afaea79",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "summary-bullet-span-bbcba214-cd2a-45b5-a97d-c9fa84d1fee4",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "患者さんの笑顔のために！無理なく長く続けられる働き方と、やりがいを見つけるヒント集"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "summary-bullet-635cd6e5-9b09-433d-a6dc-61b6dc311666",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "summary-bullet-span-064e539f-2c39-4f5f-8b30-dcb575c84cb6",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "やりがいの変化: 「治療の補助」から「生活そのものを支える」ことへ。一人ひとりの人生に深く寄り添い、信頼関係を築いてい…"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "summary-d85836d6-1c55-4f7f-b8e6-5fadd003b606",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "summary-span-bc7222a6-636d-4b9b-8320-c967a825c4ae",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "あわてず一歩ずつ、チームと情報を共有しながら進めれば大丈夫です。今日の学びを小さく実践し、次の勤務につなげていきましょう。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
